(29073, 26, 0, 'You don\'t remember me, mon? Damn da Scourge! Dey gone ta drain you of everytin dat made ya a mojo masta. Every last ounce of good... Everytin\' dat made ya a troll hero, mon!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'special_surprise SAY_EXEC_NOREM_9'),
(29073, 27, 0, 'A pact was made, $Gbrother:sister;! We vowed vengeance against the Lich King! For what he had done to us! We battled the Scourge as Forsaken, pushing them back into the plaguelands and freeing Tirisfal! You and I were champions of the Forsaken!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'special_surprise SAY_EXEC_THINK_1'),
